    },
    {
      "speaker": {
        "display_name": "Susannah DuRant",
        "matched_calendar_invitee_email": null
      },
      "text": "The cool thing here is it is actually going to detect when that attendee started talking and retroactively start recording, so you can be sure you'll get that entire monologue.",
